{"tid":1788801,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【奧燒風波】個人立場不代表球會 雲格：佢要負責任","createTime":"2019-12-19T03:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T06:38:59.000Z","uid":8968,"like":7,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"d648cdd9e8d2c930662478c2a122eaf685de5a1e","tid":1788801,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/AAzgD9KrEQmHEuPKwzpUvky4EqE=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/3SHDVVKSFPGVO2KLOTPVER2L6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FAAzgD9KrEQmHEuPKwzpUvky4EqE%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F3SHDVVKSFPGVO2KLOTPVER2L6U.jpg&h=66b6b147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/130545_9ab6d17fb43a482fc12ad6099f017417.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F130545_9ab6d17fb43a482fc12ad6099f017417.gif&h=67bdb788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.giphy.com/media/3gWB7LRl9II1PpViyg/giphy.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3gWB7LRl9II1PpViyg%2Fgiphy.webp&h=24ccc2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據英國《BBC》報道，阿仙奴傳奇領隊雲格在接受訪問時，同時提到了奧斯爾在個人社交網頁聲援受中國打壓的維吾爾人一事。但雲格則認為奧斯爾的言論只可以代表自己的觀點，而非球會的立場。<br />\n<br />\n雲格就認為奧斯爾擁有表達自己意見的權利，但這不代表球會觀點：「奧斯爾所說的言論只可以代表自己，而非阿仙奴。奧斯爾像其他人一樣擁有言論自由，他可以利用自己的名聲去表達觀點，但不一定每個人都會同意。重要的是，奧斯爾需要對自己的說話負起責任，他不必代表阿仙奴去發言。當你發表某種言論時，你必須要為自己所說過的話承擔後果。」<br />\n<br />\n另外雲格對於阿仙奴的選帥同樣表達了自己的觀點：「我一直是阿仙奴的支持者，現在我支持阿仙奴的領隊，目前是龍格保執教，所以我支持他。如果將來阿迪達執起教鞭，我也會支持阿迪達。」"},{"pid":"f9de8af74fa3be33978780bcbb126eec107101cc","tid":1788801,"uid":84363,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:25:39.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"50ad92698a05c80461eb8bf80f834f1996bb0998","tid":1788801,"uid":69568,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:28:14.000Z","msg":"含撚啦老而不"},{"pid":"d4ea2ea2d57f5af114106316fc799624969ac792","tid":1788801,"uid":28459,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:29:52.000Z","msg":"有咩責任要負？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca36605204d084076ed8073b8637330dc3528d1","tid":1788801,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"50ad92698a05c80461eb8bf80f834f1996bb0998","tid":1788801,"uid":69568,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:28:14.000Z","msg":"含撚啦老而不"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:30:08.000Z","msg":"尊重啦!"},{"pid":"5d7ab5123067c5ad176055ddbfcf5d18621b9586","tid":1788801,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:30:20.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5043538df50cf103fe99cc541629cb3b39f3948b","tid":1788801,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4ea2ea2d57f5af114106316fc799624969ac792","tid":1788801,"uid":28459,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:29:52.000Z","msg":"有咩責任要負？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"佢唔出聲，會大炒鏝3-0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c520f89920ce5023b899c0077626b1efc38b618e","tid":1788801,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4ea2ea2d57f5af114106316fc799624969ac792","tid":1788801,"uid":28459,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:29:52.000Z","msg":"有咩責任要負？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T04:06:36.000Z","msg":"+1 唔通炒咗佢咩 雲格真係 on99"},{"pid":"e7abf54b0ee8c45348d4ab95088034ea2